//!
//! Architecture:
//! ```text
//! CdpBackend
//!   ├── ChromiumProcess (owns child process)
//!   └── CdpConnection
//!         ├── write_tx: mpsc::Sender<String>  (outgoing commands)
//!         ├── pending: Arc<Mutex<HashMap<id, oneshot::Sender>>>
//!         └── reader task (spawned, reads WS messages)
